## Phase 3 — Bayesian sufficient statistics accumulation

### 🔲 Planned

- [ ] Streaming accumulator for stacker sufficient statistics:
      `weighted_sum[H,W]` = Σ $t_i x_i$,  `weight_sum[H,W]` = Σ $t_i$
- [ ] Accumulate on GPU (PyTorch) for speed
- [ ] Gamma-Poisson posterior mean as fast stacking baseline:
      $\hat{\lambda}^{(p)} = (\alpha^{(p)} + \sum_i x_i^{(p)}) / (\beta^{(p)} + n)$
- [ ] Reference PSF — weighted average of per-frame PSFs by $t_i$
- [ ] Frame metadata store — shifts, transparencies, PSF kernels, FWHMs

